[http://www.sitecom.com/en/do-you-need-help-with-your-sitecom-product-no-problem/97?product=1181&t=1&version=V1-001 Downloads] :[http://www.sitecom.com/file/wl-183-full-manual/pdf/11832 Manual] Default settings are per '''Sitecom''''s manual. :00:0E:2E ('''Edimax''') OUIs w/ sample MACs in the manual The [[Edimax BR-6524n]]'s (using RT2880) FCC docs mention this device, however, the GPL code provided by '''Sitecom''' indicate this device uses a '''5VT''' ARM chip (presumably the '''Ralink''' RT1310A). {{TechInfoDepot|Sitecom_WL-183}} ==Additional external links== *[http://us.hardware.info/productinfo/13868/sitecom-wl-183-wireless-network-300n-router#tab:overview On '''us.hardware.info''']
